-No. I'm good. You can keep it.

335
00:16:59.666 --> 00:17:00.833
We're brothers now. right?

336
00:17:01.458 --> 00:17:02.750
Brothers for life?

337
00:17:02.833 --> 00:17:03.875
Brothers for life.

338
00:17:03.958 --> 00:17:06.083
<i>-♪ We can make it if we try ♪</i>
<i>-♪ Ha-ha! ♪</i>

