but the timing couldn't be worse.

409
00:19:56.583 --> 00:19:57.916
I start shooting tomorrow.

410
00:19:58.000 --> 00:20:00.375
Come on. It's only for one night.

411
00:20:00.958 --> 00:20:02.458
- Good Lord.
