413
00:20:05.500 --> 00:20:06.500
Oh shit!

414
00:20:06.583 --> 00:20:07.541
Thank God.

415
00:20:07.625 --> 00:20:10.750
- Ugh!
- That is a wrap on Catheter Zeta-Jones.

